graphql.query:
query GetAllReservations {
  getAllReservations {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}

request.description:
Récupère toutes les réservations.

**Query GraphQL :**
```graphql
query GetAllReservations {
  getAllReservations {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}
```

graphql.query:
query GetReservation($id: ID!) {
  getReservation(id: $id) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}

request.description:
Récupère une réservation spécifique par son ID.

**Query GraphQL :**
```graphql
query GetReservation($id: ID!) {
  getReservation(id: $id) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}
```

**Variables :**
```json
{
  "id": "1"
}
```

graphql.query:
mutation CreateReservation($input: ReservationInput!) {
  createReservation(input: $input) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}

request.description:
Crée une nouvelle réservation.

**Mutation GraphQL :**
```graphql
mutation CreateReservation($input: ReservationInput!) {
  createReservation(input: $input) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}
```

**Variables :**
```json
{
  "input": {
    "dateDebut": "2024-01-15",
    "dateFin": "2024-01-20",
    "preferences": "Chambre au calme, vue sur jardin"
  }
}
```

**Format des dates :** YYYY-MM-DD

graphql.query:
mutation UpdateReservation($id: ID!, $input: ReservationInput!) {
  updateReservation(id: $id, input: $input) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}

request.description:
Met à jour une réservation existante.

**Mutation GraphQL :**
```graphql
mutation UpdateReservation($id: ID!, $input: ReservationInput!) {
  updateReservation(id: $id, input: $input) {
    id
    dateDebut
    dateFin
    preferences
  }
}
```

**Variables :**
```json
{
  "id": "1",
  "input": {
    "dateDebut": "2024-01-15",
    "dateFin": "2024-01-22",
    "preferences": "Chambre avec balcon, vue sur mer"
  }
}
```
